codingjester:

  • Shitting the bed - The action that the code you just wrote keeps doing over and over. Most likely meaning it fails miserably.

Lets use it in a sentence kids.

  • “Dammit. MyAwesomeClass just keeps shitting the bed, who the hell wrote this POS. Oh…Me.”

So says the John Bunting School of Coding…

The John Bunting School of Coding actually taught me a lot more than regular school…in most cases that is…

It’s true. I have said this.
